textBody:
This is the complete list of Olympic medalists in biathlon.

Medalists in military patrol, a precursor to biathlon, are listed separately.

Men

Individual (20 km)

Sprint (10 km)

Pursuit (12.5 km)

Mass start (15 km)

Relay (4×7.5 km)

Women

Sprint (7.5 km)

Pursuit (10 km)

Mass start (12.5 km)

Relay (4×6 km)

The women's relay event has been competed over three different distances:
* 3×7.5 km — 1992
* 4×7.5 km — 1994–2002
* 4×6 km — 2006–2014

Mixed

Relay

Medals per year
